    <item>
      <title>持续警告“排毒时期”，吹捧特朗普“呼叫”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/bessent-expects-a-detox-period-for-the-us-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长斯科特·贝斯特（Scott Bessent）警告说，随着特朗普政府转移了从政府而转向私营部门的基础，美国经济可能会有些干扰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/bessent-expects-a-detox-period-for-the-us-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 12:15:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普写信给伊朗领导人要求进行核谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-urges-iran-to-negotiate-on-nuclear-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）本周写信给伊朗的领导人，敦促该国谈判一项新的核协议，几天后，德黑兰的原子活动激增。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-urges-iran-to-negotiate-on-nuclear-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 11:51:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚的顶级外交官在与特朗普的仇恨之后寻求我们重置</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/colombia-foreign-minister-sarabia-seeks-us-reset-after-petro-trump-feud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚外交部长仍然将美国视为唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）领导下的战略伙伴，他说她想在古斯塔沃·佩特罗（Gustavo Petro）总统在社交媒体上发表的帖子引发了一场短暂的关税战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/colombia-foreign-minister-sarabia-seeks-us-reset-after-petro-trump-feud</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的比特币储备使市场失望，重视加密货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-signs-order-creating-bitcoin-reserve-and-crypto-stockpile</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统签署了一项期待已久的命令后，加密货币行业中的镇压紧张局势浮出水面，创造了战略性的比特币储备和其他数字资产的额外库存。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-signs-order-creating-bitcoin-reserve-and-crypto-stockpile</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 00:54:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
